ed to EpiDoc XML</item></change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><head lang="en"><date>257BC</date>
<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Philadelphia</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><div type="textpart" n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Ἀλέξανδρος Ζήνωνι χαίρειν. εἰ ἔρρωσαί τε καὶ ἐν τοῖς λοιποῖς <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">κατὰ νοῦν</supplied> 

    <lb n="2"/><app type="editorial"><lem>ἀπαλλάσσεις</lem><rdg>απαλλασεις</rdg></app>, εἴη ἂν ὡς ἡμεῖς βουλόμεθα. ἐρρώμεθα δὲ καὶ αὐτοί. παραγ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ινομένου</supplied> 

    <lb n="3"/>πρὸς ὑμᾶς Μυὸς ἔδοξεν ἡμῖν βέλτιον εἶναι αὐτῶι τε τῶι Μυὶ ὑπόμνημα <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ἀ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ποστεῖλαι ἐν ὧι</supplied> 

    <lb n="4"/>μνησθῆι Ἀπολλωνίωι περὶ τῆς συντάξεως ἧς ἔταξεν <choice><corr>ἡμῖν</corr><sic>ημιμ</sic></choice> Μένετ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ος. ὑ</supplied>πὸ <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ούτου δ᾽</supplied> <app type="editorial"><lem><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">οὐδὲ</supplied></lem><rdg><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἀ</supplied>πο<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">αχθῆναι ἕως</supplied></rdg></app> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τὴν</supplied> 

    <lb n="5"/>ὀφειλομένην κεκο<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">μ</unclear>ίσμεθα <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ο</unclear>ὔτε ἀφ᾽ οὗ χρόνου <choice><corr>ἐκεῖνος</corr><sic>κεινος</sic></choice> τετελεύτηκε<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν οὐδεὶς</supplied> <app type="editorial"><lem><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">ἡμῖν</supplied></lem><rdg><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τὴν σύνταξιν</supplied></rdg></app> 

    <lb n="6"/>ἀποδίδωσιν. καλῶς δ᾽ ἔχειν ὑπέλαβον καί σοι γράψαι ὅπως ἐάν τινά σου χρεί<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">αν τὰ πράγμα</supplied>-

    <lb n="7"/><app type="editorial"><lem>τα</lem><rdg><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">παρόν</supplied>τα</rdg></app> ἔχηι συναντιλάβηι φιλοτίμως καὶ ἡμῶν ἕνεκεν καὶ Μενέτου. οἷα ἂν <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">α</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἰτήσωμέν σου</supplied> 

    <lb n="8"/>βουληθέντος πάντα ἡμῖν τὰ φιλάνθρωπα ἔσται παρ᾽ Ἀπολλωνίου, καὶ ἡμεῖς <app type="editorial"><lem><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">δ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">υνησόμεθα</supplied></lem><rdg><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">δ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ιαγνωσόμεθα</supplied></rdg></app> 

    <lb n="9"/>διὰ σὲ <choice><corr>σεσῷσθαι</corr><sic>σεσωισθαι</sic></choice> καὶ ἀνεστάναι. περὶ ὧν σπουδάσομεν καὶ αὐτοὶ κα<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">θ</unclear>᾽ ὅσο<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἡμῖ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear> κ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">αὶ δυνατὸν</supplied> 

    <lb n="10"/>τὰς χάριτας ἀποδιδόναι σοι. 

    <lb n="11"/><space extent="unknown" unit="character" dim="horizontal"/> εὐτύχει. 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

